CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 28, 1962, pg. A11 reads: "Dynamic Danettes Slate Rocket ball Cabaret May 6 - Planning "Rocket Ball" - These members of the Dynamic Danettes Civic Club are planning their "Rocket Ball" cabaret, Sunday, May 6, at the Ming Tree Supper Club (Town House). First row: President Ida Jones, left, and Gladys Lawson, Back row: Carrie Ralph, Florence Hutchinson, chairman, and Betty Culberson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of five Dynamic Danettes club members, from left, first row: Ida Jones and Gladys Lawson; back row: Carrie Ralph, Florence Hutchinson, and Betty Culberson, posed in interior with brick fireplace
